<section xmlns="http://xml.house.gov/schemas/uslm/1.0" style="-uslm-lc:I80" id="idefcdef3a-3a6e-11f1-addd-bbaf0b3f68e9" identifier="/us/usc/t7/s5814"><num value="5814">§ 5814.</num><heading> Authorization of appropriations</heading><content>
<p style="-uslm-lc:I11" class="indent0">There are authorized to be appropriated to carry out this part $40,000,000 for each of fiscal years 2013 through 2023. Of amounts appropriated to carry out this part for a fiscal year, not less than $15,000,000, or not less than two thirds of any such appropriation, whichever is greater, shall be used to carry out sections 5811 and 5812 of this title.</p>
</content><sourceCredit id="idefcdef3b-3a6e-11f1-addd-bbaf0b3f68e9">(<ref href="/us/pl/101/624/tXVI/s1624">Pub. L. 101–624, title XVI, § 1624</ref>, <date date="1990-11-28">Nov. 28, 1990</date>, <ref href="/us/stat/104/3739">104 Stat. 3739</ref>; <ref href="/us/pl/102/237/tIV/s408">Pub. L. 102–237, title IV, § 408</ref>, <date date="1991-12-13">Dec. 13, 1991</date>, <ref href="/us/stat/105/1865">105 Stat. 1865</ref>; <ref href="/us/pl/113/79/tVII/s7201">Pub. L. 113–79, title VII, § 7201</ref>, <date date="2014-02-07">Feb. 7, 2014</date>, <ref href="/us/stat/128/880">128 Stat. 880</ref>; <ref href="/us/pl/115/334/tVII/s7201">Pub. L. 115–334, title VII, § 7201</ref>, <date date="2018-12-20">Dec. 20, 2018</date>, <ref href="/us/stat/132/4803">132 Stat. 4803</ref>.)</sourceCredit>
